data.description: Welcome to the highly desirable community of Watergrass. This elegant perfectly maintained house offers luxury living, open floor plan, stylish upgrades, stunning backyard views and modern finishes. The house has 3 Bedrooms, one of which can be used as an office/study room and 2 full Bathrooms. The open layout is a combination of kitchen/dining/living area with plenty of room, lots of warm natural light completed by a bright LVP flooring and provides a great space for entertaining. The kitchen features beautiful granite countertops, subway style backsplash, large kitchen island, lots of cabinet space and it is perfect for exploring your chefs dreams! The large Owner suite has upgraded tray ceilings, stylish walk in shower with wall tiles and granite counter dual vanity. Step outside through the triple sliding doors and you will find an extended covered fully screened in lanai, amazing water/nature views where you can relax, have your morning cup of coffee or entertain with friends and family! The two car garage is upgraded with epoxy coated flooring.  Enjoy all the amenities that this community provides - two resort style pools, clubhouse, gym, tennis and basketball courts, playgrounds, splash zone and a dog park.  Watergrass is conveniently located close to a great schools, I-75, Wiregrass Mall, Tampa Premium Outlets, The Grove, restaurants, hospitals and the best Wesley Chapel has to offer. Don’t wait and book your showing now!
